## Quick Start

1. Review your workspace: `ls ~/.openclaw/workspace/`
2. Configure API keys: `openclaw-setup`
3. Validate installation: `openclaw-validate`
4. Start OpenClaw: `openclaw start`

## Workspace Layout

```
~/.openclaw/workspace/
  goals/        - Project goals and objectives
  tools/        - Custom tools and scripts
  context/      - Context files for agents
  hardprompts/  - System prompts and templates
  args/         - Argument files for commands
  memory/       - Persistent memory and logs
  data/         - Data storage (SQLite DB, etc.)
```

